Dedicato al centenario
di Mikhail Kotsiubinski

6
00:00:31,0 --> 00:00:33,150
Oleksa!

7
00:00:42,40 --> 00:00:43,359
Mi senti?

8
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:49,638
Oleksa, vieni a mangiare!

9
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:53,75
Spostati, Ivanko, spostati!

10
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:06,951
Vieni fuori! Oleksa, vieni fuori!
Fratello, vieni fuori!

11
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:49,34
